617
0:41:32,623 --> 0:41:35,159
Atta boy!
Whoops-a-daisy.


618
0:41:35,159 --> 0:41:36,594
Charming child.


619
0:41:36,594 --> 0:41:45,269
Yes.


620
0:41:45,269 --> 0:41:46,57
Mr. Thurber, you better check with Mills


621
0:41:46,57 --> 0:41:47,838
about that last
carload of ties.


